commit.message: Add mutant 0.11.22 gem dependency
Add Memoizable::Memory#marshal_load test
Add Memoizable::Memory#key? test
Add Memoizable::Memory#fetch test

Fix Memoizable::Memory#[]= alive mutation

* Add Memoizable::Memory#[]= test

Fix Memoizable::Memory#[] alive mutation

* Add Memoizable::Memory#[] test
* Refactor Memoizable::Memory#[] to be simpler
Fix Memoizable::Memory#initialize alive mutations

Fix Memoizable::MethodBuilder#set_method_visibility to be simpler

* This uses a simpler primitive method.
Fix Memoizable::MethodBuilder#create_memoized_method alive mutation

Change Memoizable::MethodBuilder#call to no longer remove methods

* This may cause warnings in older versions of ruby, but it does not
  affect newer versions of ruby.

Refactor Memoizable::Memory#fetch to be simpler

* It is not necessary to call self#[]=, which does redundant work, than
  to call @memory#[]= directory.

Refactor Memoizable::MethodBuilder#initialize to use accessor

* Also use the local descendant variable instead of the ivar in
  #initialize.
Refactor Memoizable::InstanceMethods#freeze to be simpler
Fix Memoizable::Memory test to use more consistent variable names
Fix GitHub Actions artifact upload to not warn if no files found

Remove Memoizable::ModuleMethods#included

* This method was not necessary to include Memoizable into the
  descendant. Normal module inclusion was sufficient.
Change Memoizable::Memory.new memory parameter to be a Hash
Change Memoizable::Memory.new constructor to accept memory parameter
Refactor Memoizable::Memory#[]= to be simpler
Refactor Memoizable::Memory#fetch test setup
Fix Memoizable::MethodBuilder#call to not output to stderr
Remove Memoizable::Memory#key?
Remove Memoizable::ModuleMethods#memoized?
